This package contains updated Lithuanian time zone (Europe/Vilnius: in 1998
Lithuanian time zone changed to CET; in 1999 -- back to EET; in 2000 -- to
EET without daylight savings).

Files
-----

Europe/Vilnius      compiled time zone data
lithuania           this contains all required data to compile the updated
                    time zone
europe.diff         unified diff for `europe' file as found in tzdata2000d
                    package by by Arthur David Olson et.al.


Installation
------------

Either overwrite your old Europe/Vilnius in /usr/share/zoneinfo (for
Slackware distribution, other distributions might use other directories)
or use `zic' to do that:

  # zic lithuania

You can then use `timeconfig' or a similair program to set you local time
zone to Europe/Vilnius.


